These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, chaman
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar       | chaman       | aristoff |
| Game         | scrabble | monopoly  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Beverage   | water       | mirinda      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
City: nizza, berlin
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, soul
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
2 different games are played: canasta, go
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| City      | berlin     | nizza |
| Music-Genre           | d&b | soul      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Game         | canasta | go     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
2 different games are played: poker, whist
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person playing whist##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby      | hiking | puzzles  |
| Flower          | sunflower    | aconite   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Game     | whist     | poker |

