There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, game
House: futuristic, ranch-style
1. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the malaysian is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Nationality      | japanese       | malaysian |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Cigar           | game | dannemann    |
| House   | futuristic           | ranch-style   |

