City: nizza, hamburg
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, pilot
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Food         | pineapple | asparagus   |
| City   | nizza | hamburg       |
| Job         | software-developer   | pilot |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike     |

