2 different pets are kept: mouse, goat
There 2 different types of food: corn, onion
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, badminton
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person eating onion is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person eating corn is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| Hobby         | reading            | board-games  |
| Pet           | goat | mouse |
| Food   | corn           | onion       |
| Sport     | ice-hockey            | badminton        |

