The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Color      | chestnut        | light-blue        |
| Transport          | train | quad-bike       |
| Hobby         | puzzles    | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | scientific  |

