.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, electronic
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, pink
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who likes white is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | mexican | egyptian     |
| Music-Genre   | classical          | electronic |
| Color           | white          | pink    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 